HEADWORD: Hangnest
<hw>Hang"nest`</hw> <pr>(-n⟦ecr⟧st`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>A nest that hangs like a bag or pocket.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A bird which builds such a nest; a
